                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>7th Sep 23 Elul 5623</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>The <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Many thanks for the<lb/> photographs you so kindly sent me<lb/> in\n                your favor of <date>1st</date>. One copy<lb/>\n                <persName>Mrs De Sola</persName> will give to <persName>Mrs J A\n                Joseph</persName><lb/> as you promised her one—the other<lb/>\n                <add>לָעַד בַּסֵּפֶר יוּחַק. בְּרִית עולָם בַּל יֻמְחַק. אֶת אַבְרָהָם וְאֶת\n                    יִצְחָק</add><lb/> which means that both my wife<lb/> and myself will be proud\n                to preserve<lb/> in our album the lineaments of<lb/> one we so highly esteem, and\n                who<lb/> deserves so well of <placeName>Israel</placeName>. I wish<lb/> with the\n                    <persName>Payton</persName> I could add the<lb/> scriptural <add>והיה הוא\n                    ותמורתו</add>—but I cannot<lb/> have the pleasure of <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >exchanging</hi></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3v11w58b/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
